<h1>Camera Space - Demo 10<a class="headerlink" href="#camera-space-demo-10" title="Permalink to this heading">¶</a></h1>
<section id="purpose">
<h2>Purpose<a class="headerlink" href="#purpose" title="Permalink to this heading">¶</a></h2>
<p>Graphical programs in which the viewer never “moves” are boring.
Model a virtual “camera”, and let the user move the camera around
in the scene.  In this picture, notice that the purple paddle
is no longer on the left side of the screen, but towards the right,
horizontally.</p>
